'''Tarkin's Teeth''' was an area of [[Carida/Legends|Carida]] three hundred [[Kilometer/Legends|kilometers]] from the [[Carida Academy/Legends|Academy of Carida]]. Mountainous and desolate, by [[0 ABY/Legends|0.5 ABY]] it had been used as a military training ground for several centuries.

